50|$|After {{his army}} service Campbell turned his {{attention}} to business and politics in Northern Ireland. He became the managing director of two <b>flax</b> <b>spinning</b> companies; Henry Campbell and Co., and Messrs Laverty and Co. Ltd and was appointed Deputy Flax Controller for Northern Ireland in 1940.|$|E
